description:
Danny interviews author & TV personality, Brandi Glanville (#RHOBH, Celebrity Apprentice), about all things Real Housewives, working with Trump, her books, AND she drops a Coyote Ugly bombshell. Danny also discusses JT and ridiculous Instagram sponsorships. The interview with Brandi starts at 11:23. :)
